    <description>Flow to be used with SoftPhone Layout in order to create a case and redirect to the case
V1. Removed Puzzel queue mapping and added hardcoded Theme group because Hjelpemidler only has one
V2. Added Recordtype handling and enquirylog to collect Caller number and store on Case</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
    <formulas>
        <description>Formula to determine the type of input from the IVR. Either, PHONE_NUMBER, PERSON_IDENT or ORG_IDENT.</description>
        <name>INPUT_TYPE</name>
        <dataType>String</dataType>
        <expression>CASE(LEN({!Search}),
11, &apos;PERSON_IDENT&apos;,
9, &apos;ORG_IDENT&apos;,
&apos;PHONE_NUMBER&apos;
)</expression>
    </formulas>
